1
00:01:43,620 --> 00:01:46,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Commencing final graft.</font>

2
00:01:53,140 --> 00:01:54,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's stable.</font>

3
00:01:54,590 --> 00:01:57,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once this phase is complete, 
Knives will reawaken.</font>

4
00:01:57,730 --> 00:01:59,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When he does—</font>

5
00:02:01,080 --> 00:02:05,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He will absolutely and utterly 
return this world to nothing.</font>

6
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:12,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean he has the power he needs 
to enact the Genesis Flood Big Fall?</font>

7
00:02:12,110 --> 00:02:14,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More than enough.</font>

8
00:02:14,590 --> 00:02:18,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After merging with countless plants...</font>

9
00:02:18,050 --> 00:02:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he is a cluster of unfathomable energy.</font>

10
00:02:21,650 --> 00:02:22,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And so...</font>

11
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:27,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Knives will write 
a new Book of Genesis.</font>

12
00:02:27,460 --> 00:02:30,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He will become a true god.</font>

13
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed.</font>

14
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:35,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a long, long journey.</font>

15
00:02:35,980 --> 00:02:39,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All that remains of Knives's followers</font>

16
00:02:39,010 --> 00:02:44,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are you, Elendira, Ninelives, and myself.</font>

17
00:02:45,860 --> 00:02:49,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vash the Stampede must be returned to us.</font>

18
00:02:49,810 --> 00:02:52,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The twins are only complete when together.</font>

19
00:02:52,540 --> 00:02:58,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They need each other to fill
 what's missing of themselves.</font>

20
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:01,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Same for the Eye of Michael.</font>

21
00:03:05,230 --> 00:03:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Ninelives...</font>

22
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:09,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's odd, isn't it?</font>

23
00:03:09,350 --> 00:03:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Knives is about to achieve his goal
of turning this planet</font>

24
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">into a paradise for plants, but...</font>

25
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:21,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Somehow, he seems to be sad about it.</font>

26
00:03:22,810 --> 00:03:24,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me, Lord Knives.</font>

27
00:03:24,870 --> 00:03:27,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are we, well...</font>

28
00:03:27,710 --> 00:03:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">not good enough?</font>

29
00:03:31,700 --> 00:03:36,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's right here,
yet he feels so distant...</font>

30
00:03:37,640 --> 00:03:39,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope I'm just overthinking.</font>

31
00:03:42,990 --> 00:03:44,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this...</font>

32
00:03:44,390 --> 00:03:45,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

33
00:03:45,690 --> 00:03:46,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel it.</font>

34
00:03:46,770 --> 00:03:47,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feel what?</font>

35
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:50,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vash the Stampede.</font>

36
00:03:50,350 --> 00:03:51,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this?</font>

37
00:03:51,900 --> 00:03:55,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. He's cornered 
and trying to lure us out.</font>

38
00:03:55,420 --> 00:03:57,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That saves us the hassle of looking for him.</font>

39
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:58,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's go.</font>

40
00:03:58,730 --> 00:04:00,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, hold on. You can't just—</font>

41
00:04:01,050 --> 00:04:04,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doctor, you just shut up and fly the Ark.</font>

42
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:07,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Elendira, where is he? 
Where's Vash the Stampede?</font>

43
00:04:08,700 --> 00:04:10,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's at...</font>

44
00:04:18,030 --> 00:04:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How'd it go, Vash?</font>

45
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:23,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, pretty sure I got through 
to him... I think.</font>

46
00:04:23,740 --> 00:04:26,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then now we wait.</font>

47
00:04:27,860 --> 00:04:32,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is where you first landed, right?</font>

48
00:04:32,470 --> 00:04:34,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where our journey...</font>

49
00:04:36,110 --> 00:04:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where this hell began.</font>

50
00:04:44,660 --> 00:04:46,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could you?</font>

51
00:04:47,100 --> 00:04:49,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You killed even <i>Rem!</i></font>

52
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:50,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're my accomplice.</font>

53
00:04:53,350 --> 00:04:58,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right, Vash?</font>

54
00:05:00,590 --> 00:05:04,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the appropriate place
 to put an end to everything.</font>

55
00:05:04,870 --> 00:05:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This hell, our journey...</font>

56
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:10,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rem's regrets.</font>

57
00:05:13,580 --> 00:05:18,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Let's settle things
with Millions Knives.</font>

58
00:05:20,060 --> 00:05:26,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still... what really is this "paradise 
for plants" he kept talking about?</font>

59
00:05:26,660 --> 00:05:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

60
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:31,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, he said he wanted to wipe out
 all humans on the planet</font>

61
00:05:31,550 --> 00:05:34,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and make every plant an Independent.</font>

62
00:05:35,270 --> 00:05:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But is that truly a paradise for plants?</font>

63
00:05:40,820 --> 00:05:43,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that what the plants want?</font>

64
00:05:44,340 --> 00:05:45,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know.</font>

65
00:05:46,180 --> 00:05:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some emotions come through to me.</font>

66
00:05:48,670 --> 00:05:52,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But their inner hearts,</font>

67
00:05:52,670 --> 00:05:56,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what they truly think and desire...</font>

68
00:05:56,100 --> 00:05:57,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not even I can know that for sure.</font>

69
00:05:58,370 --> 00:06:04,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you really don't know,
then nobody does.</font>

70
00:06:04,330 --> 00:06:07,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then what is Knives basing all of this on?</font>

71
00:06:07,570 --> 00:06:09,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just what he wants.</font>

72
00:06:10,260 --> 00:06:12,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What Meryl said before...</font>

73
00:06:13,150 --> 00:06:15,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The desire to learn is what's important.</font>

74
00:06:17,220 --> 00:06:23,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have I really tried to understand plants?</font>

75
00:06:24,330 --> 00:06:26,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That'd include Knives...</font>

76
00:06:28,250 --> 00:06:32,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, did I say something weird?</font>

77
00:06:32,250 --> 00:06:33,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, no.</font>

78
00:06:35,780 --> 00:06:38,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no need for that.</font>

79
00:06:39,390 --> 00:06:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who'd blame us for not wanting
 to understand that?</font>

80
00:06:46,340 --> 00:06:49,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't see anything yet.</font>

81
00:06:51,110 --> 00:06:54,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meryl? Is something wrong?</font>

82
00:06:54,650 --> 00:06:55,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Three years.</font>

83
00:06:55,790 --> 00:06:57,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

84
00:06:57,050 --> 00:07:01,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It feels like a long, 
long time has passed...</font>

85
00:07:02,350 --> 00:07:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's only been three years.</font>

86
00:07:04,630 --> 00:07:07,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, since Lost JuLai?</font>

87
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:10,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One, two, three...</font>

88
00:07:10,670 --> 00:07:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, you're right! Only three years!</font>

89
00:07:14,990 --> 00:07:18,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It feels like such a long time ago.</font>

90
00:07:18,250 --> 00:07:20,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It weighs on even us like that.</font>

91
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:23,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For Vash, these three years...</font>

92
00:07:23,840 --> 00:07:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, the past 150 years...</font>

93
00:07:27,650 --> 00:07:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just how long and painful
was that journey?</font>

94
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:37,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can only hope that wherever he reaches</font>

95
00:07:37,150 --> 00:07:41,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">at the end of this long,
 torturous road is peaceful.</font>

96
00:08:13,310 --> 00:08:14,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Razlo?</font>

97
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All these fools lack faith.</font>

98
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take this.</font>

99
00:08:20,980 --> 00:08:23,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to vindicate myself.</font>

100
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:27,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that for?</font>

101
00:08:27,490 --> 00:08:30,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember, don't kill him.</font>

102
00:08:32,570 --> 00:08:37,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you hear what I just said? 
I'm going to vindicate myself.</font>

103
00:08:37,970 --> 00:08:42,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vash the Stampede needs 
to be punished appropriately.</font>

104
00:08:42,820 --> 00:08:43,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Punished?</font>

105
00:08:44,660 --> 00:08:47,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I'm going to use this.</font>

106
00:08:47,980 --> 00:08:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must show how deep my faith runs.</font>

107
00:09:09,150 --> 00:09:12,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for your kind invitation.</font>

108
00:09:13,470 --> 00:09:18,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or rather, shouldn't you be thanking me 
for coming all the way out here?</font>

109
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:22,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Legato Bluesummers. 
You're not the one we're here for.</font>

110
00:09:22,870 --> 00:09:25,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that, of course.</font>

111
00:09:25,030 --> 00:09:28,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if you want to stop Lord Knives,</font>

112
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:31,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'll have to get through me first.</font>

113
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:36,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a cliché. I'm almost 
disgusted with myself—</font>

114
00:09:38,430 --> 00:09:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So hasty. People don't like that.</font>

115
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:41,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever!</font>

116
00:09:59,820 --> 00:10:01,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Warnings are useless.</font>

117
00:10:01,770 --> 00:10:04,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're going to shoot, shoot to kill.</font>

118
00:10:09,460 --> 00:10:10,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa there.</font>

119
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Razlo the Tri-Punisher of Death...</font>

120
00:10:13,290 --> 00:10:15,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We raised you. Is this how you thank us?</font>

121
00:10:15,990 --> 00:10:18,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my way of returning the favor!</font>

122
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:23,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, my name isn't Razlo! It's Livio!</font>

123
00:10:32,810 --> 00:10:34,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you fighting with that weapon?</font>

124
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must volunteer to bear 
the cross, feel the pain,</font>

125
00:10:39,550 --> 00:10:43,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and climb the hill of Golgotha 
subjected to ridicule and scorn.</font>

126
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:47,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And when I reach the site 
of my execution, I shall perish.</font>

127
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:56,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should study up on the 
history of Earth. Of mankind.</font>

128
00:10:56,300 --> 00:10:59,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll get right on that...
after I take you down!</font>

129
00:11:19,620 --> 00:11:23,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this all we can do? 
Just watch from here?</font>

130
00:11:23,370 --> 00:11:26,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what can we even do from here?</font>

131
00:11:26,030 --> 00:11:30,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know! I know, but...</font>

132
00:11:35,530 --> 00:11:38,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's almost like we could just hop on.</font>

133
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:39,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

134
00:11:40,020 --> 00:11:40,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

135
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:42,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

136
00:11:42,430 --> 00:11:43,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

137
00:11:43,930 --> 00:11:44,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

138
00:11:49,830 --> 00:11:51,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vash the Stampede!</font>

139
00:11:51,940 --> 00:11:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Legato Bluesummers!</font>

140
00:12:41,460 --> 00:12:46,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stupidity in numbers. 
What a useless pile of big oafs.</font>

141
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But they're almost invincible.</font>

142
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:53,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've gotta take out the blue-haired freak
 and get to the Ark...</font>

143
00:12:53,030 --> 00:12:56,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll handle Ninelives. 
Nico, please help Vash!</font>

144
00:12:56,460 --> 00:12:57,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

145
00:12:58,170 --> 00:12:59,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't fell them, but I'll hold them off!</font>

146
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:01,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't push yourself too hard, Livio.</font>

147
00:13:01,580 --> 00:13:03,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You watch out too, Nico!</font>

148
00:13:03,390 --> 00:13:06,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not supposed to worry
 about your big brother, dumbass!</font>

149
00:13:09,140 --> 00:13:10,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take this...</font>

150
00:13:12,560 --> 00:13:14,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and go down!</font>

151
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:28,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That idiot.</font>

152
00:13:31,420 --> 00:13:35,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I said, shoot to kill, okay?</font>

153
00:13:54,290 --> 00:14:00,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vash the Stampede,
you still don't want to kill anyone.</font>

154
00:14:00,540 --> 00:14:01,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

155
00:14:01,640 --> 00:14:06,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That won't do. 
You have to <i>want</i> to kill me.</font>

156
00:14:07,330 --> 00:14:11,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the only way to cleanse
your sin-soaked body.</font>

157
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:19,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From the transgression of tormenting and
saddening Lord Knives for over 150 years.</font>

158
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know all too well how saddened 
he was when you betrayed him.</font>

159
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:29,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be stupid. Nai would never—</font>

160
00:14:29,040 --> 00:14:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Knives <i>is</i> sad! 
Why don't you understand?!</font>

161
00:14:35,760 --> 00:14:39,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you ever even stopped 
to think about how he feels?</font>

162
00:14:41,270 --> 00:14:46,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instead of just forcing your feelings
and empty words onto him...</font>

163
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:53,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you ever really, actually thought 
about how Lord Knives feels?</font>

164
00:14:55,150 --> 00:14:58,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you, even once?</font>

165
00:14:58,990 --> 00:15:01,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vash the Stampede!</font>

166
00:15:09,260 --> 00:15:10,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wolfwood...</font>

167
00:15:10,180 --> 00:15:14,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bluetop! I didn't realize 
you were such a brat.</font>

168
00:15:14,140 --> 00:15:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

169
00:15:15,380 --> 00:15:17,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how much you talk,</font>

170
00:15:17,730 --> 00:15:20,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">people never truly comprehend one another!</font>

171
00:15:20,780 --> 00:15:22,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grow up!</font>

172
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:27,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... can you teach me?</font>

173
00:15:28,110 --> 00:15:30,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to understand.</font>

174
00:15:30,590 --> 00:15:32,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to try to understand.</font>

175
00:15:32,640 --> 00:15:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What you're thinking...</font>

176
00:15:35,350 --> 00:15:39,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What Nai is really thinking.</font>

177
00:15:42,860 --> 00:15:45,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, I'll teach you.</font>

178
00:15:45,530 --> 00:15:48,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you can defeat me, I will then!</font>

179
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:44,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wolfwood!</font>

180
00:16:44,760 --> 00:16:45,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is...</font>

181
00:16:46,940 --> 00:16:48,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the end!</font>

182
00:17:06,670 --> 00:17:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bluetop...</font>

183
00:17:10,880 --> 00:17:14,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be honest. That was close.</font>

184
00:17:15,220 --> 00:17:21,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'll be generous. 
I'll tell you how I really feel.</font>

185
00:17:23,900 --> 00:17:25,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wolfwood...</font>

186
00:17:25,950 --> 00:17:28,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Eye of Michael's teachings are simple.</font>

187
00:17:29,360 --> 00:17:33,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say, "Praise our two gods."</font>

188
00:17:34,410 --> 00:17:39,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two of them. The first is,
 of course, Lord Knives.</font>

189
00:17:39,770 --> 00:17:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The other is...</font>

190
00:17:41,370 --> 00:17:44,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Vash the Stampede.</font>

191
00:17:47,740 --> 00:17:51,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I met our god Lord Knives
and was fulfilled.</font>

192
00:17:52,300 --> 00:17:57,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am compelled to believe, worship, 
and follow the word of Lord Knives.</font>

193
00:17:58,170 --> 00:18:01,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How blessed that is.</font>

194
00:18:02,050 --> 00:18:05,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And on top of that, 
to have yet another god!</font>

195
00:18:05,860 --> 00:18:10,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's... It's so wonderful!</font>

196
00:18:10,990 --> 00:18:13,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which is why, Vash the Stampede...</font>

197
00:18:13,970 --> 00:18:18,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't wait to meet you!</font>

198
00:18:19,450 --> 00:18:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you even...</font>

199
00:18:22,650 --> 00:18:27,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yet you turned out to be 
the god of betrayal.</font>

200
00:18:28,080 --> 00:18:33,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You saddened and tormented 
our other god, Lord Knives!</font>

201
00:18:34,690 --> 00:18:37,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your sins are too grave...</font>

202
00:18:40,120 --> 00:18:44,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And so you must be punished.</font>

203
00:18:47,290 --> 00:18:51,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must pay the highest price thinkable, 
endure the worst pain imaginable.</font>

204
00:18:51,930 --> 00:18:57,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only then will you be cleansed of your sin.</font>

205
00:18:57,430 --> 00:18:58,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What...</font>

206
00:18:58,370 --> 00:19:02,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, when you are pure
of heart and body at last,</font>

207
00:19:02,060 --> 00:19:09,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you will finally be ready to stand 
beside Lord Knives as our other god.</font>

208
00:19:11,190 --> 00:19:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our gods will finally descend upon 
the Eye of Michael and wipe out the world.</font>

209
00:19:18,020 --> 00:19:22,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, could there be any greater happiness?</font>

210
00:19:24,180 --> 00:19:28,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The hour of judgment
is upon you, Lord Vash.</font>

211
00:19:28,350 --> 00:19:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The only thing you can move now 
is your trigger finger.</font>

212
00:19:33,060 --> 00:19:35,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Punisher will soon die.</font>

213
00:19:36,620 --> 00:19:38,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to save him...</font>

214
00:19:39,070 --> 00:19:44,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must, by your own will, 
pull that trigger and kill me.</font>

215
00:19:46,940 --> 00:19:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Needle-noggin...</font>

216
00:19:51,050 --> 00:19:55,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, kill me! Kill a human!</font>

217
00:19:55,820 --> 00:19:58,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For the first time of your own will!</font>

218
00:20:11,710 --> 00:20:14,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my Golgotha.</font>

219
00:20:16,470 --> 00:20:21,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Lord Knives will know 
how deep my faith is.</font>

220
00:21:05,970 --> 00:21:10,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someone has to bring the fangs. 
Otherwise, someone else pays in tears.</i></font>

221
00:22:11,020 --> 00:22:14,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#fffeff">Year 113, July 20th
One day until the immigrant fleet arrives</font></b></font></font>

222
00:23:47,450 --> 00:23:51,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's you. Just you and me.</font>

223
00:23:52,260 --> 00:23:54,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all this world needs.</font>

